text: Tanwarin in 2019 Tanwarin Sukkhapisit (, , ) is a Thai filmmaker and politician. In the 2019 Thai general election, Tanwarin was elected to the Thai parliament representing the Future Forward Party, becoming Thailand's first ever openly transgender MP in the House of Representatives.
